data.description: Price reduced t below 2023 DCAD market value. Charming, spacious home in desirable Little Forest Hills! Wonderful floor plan with 2BR down and 1BR up. French doors lead you to generously sized backyard, and back patio invites you to relax and unwind in serene outdoor setting. 2nd story presents an exciting opportunity for customization and can easily be transformed into a stunning primary bedroom, complete with en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. Imagine having your own private retreat at the top of the house, offering both comfort and privacy, with complete views of backyard from balcony. This home offers a wonderful combination of a peaceful neighborhood setting with convenient access to White Rock Lake, Dallas Arboretum and all that East Dallas has to offer. With its spacious layout, potential for a luxurious primary bedroom suite, inviting backyard, and desirable location, this property isn't one to miss!
